/**
 * Cross-language parity: the TS domain port must reproduce every golden case
 * in contracts/fixtures/ EXACTLY. The fixtures were generated by
 * tools/gen_fixtures.py from the live Python domain/ -- they are the arbiter
 * of correctness, not readability preferences (MIGRATION_PLAN note #4).
 *
 * Exact equality, floats included: both sides are IEEE-754 doubles and JSON
 * round-trips them shortest-exact. A tolerance would let a wrong formula pass.
 *
 * CI runs this beside `python tools/gen_fixtures.py --check`; together they
 * detect Python drift AND port drift from the same goldens.
 */

